ExpiredContracts is a BusinessTask
    owned by bl

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for FinancialsViewer, ApplicationAdministrator, FinancialsProcessor, BillingManager,Billing
                category is "Analysis"
                report name is "Expired Contracts"
                Description
                    Generate list of expired pricing contracts. Contracts are agreements established for a time period with a customer on a one-to-one basis that determines pricing arrangements.   
            Reports
                ExpiredContractsReport

    Parameters
        OplCompany              is a BillingCompany
        OplBegDate              is Date
        OplEndDate              is Date
        FrAddSubtract           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                AddDays      value is "A"
                    default label is "Add days"
                SubtractDays value is "S"
                    default label is "Subtract days"
        FrDays                  is Numeric size 3
        ToAddSubtract           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                AddDays      value is "A"
                    default label is "Add days"
                SubtractDays value is "S"
                    default label is "Subtract days"
        ToDays                  is Numeric size 3
        FileName                is AlphaUpper size 30

    Parameter Rules
        OplCompany
            required
        FrAddSubtract
        	initial value is "S"
            default to "S"
        ToAddSubtract
        	initial value is "S"
            default to "S"

    Actions
        ExpiredContracts is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
